                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7455" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1172</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2283 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雪中送炭还是雪上加霜？——迅游科技商誉减值之殇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Deliver fuel or add frost in the snow? —— The pain of goodwill impairment in Sichuan Xunyou Network Technology Co., Ltd.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王珮，姜仁杰，孙嘉欣，王瑶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（北京）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四川迅游网络科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">迅游科技；并购估值；商誉减值；商誉质量判断；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xunyou Network Technology Co., Ltd.; merger and acquisition valuation; goodwill impairment; goodwill quality judgment; corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业板并购热潮在并购重组制度改革之后逐渐达到高峰，高溢价、高商誉和高业绩承诺成为创业板并购中的普遍现象。随着大多数上市企业业绩承诺期结束，巨额商誉减值现象屡见不鲜，创业板成为“重灾区”。迅游科技于2015年在创业板上市，作为“网游加速器第一股”、“四川互联网第一股”，其并购狮之吼时便引起不少关注，而后突然的商誉“爆雷”更是引发业界震动。迅游科技本想通过并购达到雪中送炭的效果，躲过业绩下滑的寒冬，未料此举却是雪上加霜，甚至导致公司经营业绩系列“雪崩”。随着2021年其高溢价并购狮之吼产生的巨额商誉悉数减值完毕，迅游科技此番并购之路也算尘埃落定。本案例分别对迅游科技并购活动动因和对业务结构及财务业绩的影响、高商誉带来巨大风险的原因、商誉减值的影响以及公司内部治理等问题进行全面探究，旨在引导学生关注创业板上市公司并购过程中商誉的“水分”，思考爆雷现象的本质原因及其经济后果，同时向学生强调公司内部治理的重要性。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">After the reform of merger and reorganization system, the boom of merger and reorganization in GEM has gradually reached a peak. High premium, high goodwill and high performance commitment have also become common phenomena in GEM merger and acquisition. Nowadays, with the end of the performance commitment period of most listed enterprises, the phenomenon of huge goodwill impairment is common, especially the GEM has become a &quot;disaster area&quot;. Xunyou Network Technology Co., Ltd. was listed on the GEM in 2015. As &quot;the first online game accelerator stock&quot; and &quot;the first Internet stock in Sichuan&quot;, its merger and acquisition attracted a lot of attention when the lion shouted, and then the sudden goodwill &quot;thunder&quot; caused shock in the industry.Xunyou Network Technology Co., Ltd. intended to achieve the effect of timely help through mergers and acquisitions, avoid the winter of declining performance, unexpected this move is worse, and even triggered the company&#39;s business performance series &quot;avalanche&quot;. With the huge goodwill generated by its acquisition of Lion Roar at a high premium in 2021 all wiped out, Xunyou&#39;s acquisition of the road to the dust. In this case, the reasons for Xunyou&#39;s merger and acquisition activities and their impact on business structure and financial performance, the reasons for the great risks brought by high goodwill, the impact of goodwill impairment and the company&#39;s internal governance are comprehensively explored. The purpose of this case is to guide students to pay attention to the &quot;moisture&quot; of goodwill in the merger and acquisition process of listed companies on GEM, and to think about the essential causes and economic consequences of the phenomenon of mine explosion. At the same time, the importance of internal governance is emphasized to students.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务报表分析》、《财务会计理论与实务》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商誉特点；创业板特点；并购动因理论；企业价值评估理论；商誉减值；商誉的后续计量；有效市场假说；关联交易；商业伦理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
